{"tid":691300,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"麻省總醫院：Loris Karius歐冠決賽中出現腦震盪","createTime":"2018-06-05T15:07:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-06T07:10:42.000Z","uid":76310,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6cf724ac33dae2e2d28a08d5cd5c90cc0cf103ab","tid":691300,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T15:07:00.000Z","msg":"麻省總醫院：Loris Karius歐冠決賽中出現腦震盪<br />\n<br />\n麻省總醫院官方確認，利物浦門將Loris Karius在歐冠決賽中出現腦震盪。<br />\n<br />\n麻省總醫院稱，Loris Karius在5月31日接受了醫院的檢查，在通過對錄像和相關細節的分析，以及球員賽后的症狀，Loris Karius在歐冠決賽中出現腦震盪情況。這有可能是影響他隨後表現的原因之一。<br />\n<br />\nLoris Karius在歐冠決賽中受到了皇馬隊長拉莫斯的衝撞，但是回放顯示，拉莫斯在衝撞Loris Karius之前受到了範迪克的推搡，範迪克也承認了自己對拉莫斯有動作，因此歐足聯表示不會處罰拉莫斯。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/1528145682520e6e4429e10\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fp3.pstatp.com%2Flarge%2Fpgc-image%2F1528145682520e6e4429e10&h=e9116157&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4d1f5d4edf6b2e8893094eeccadb02a1f060cba1","tid":691300,"uid":54025,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T15:10:29.000Z","msg":"有事就躝出場啦<br />\n<br />\n死頂搞到做國際笑話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3688bb5e64cf01c1570bb4d4c78291922c052c55","tid":691300,"uid":86756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d1f5d4edf6b2e8893094eeccadb02a1f060cba1","tid":691300,"uid":54025,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T15:10:29.000Z","msg":"有事就躝出場啦<br />\n<br />\n死頂搞到做國際笑話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T15:28:31.000Z","msg":"收左錢唔做野點得呀<br />\n你射完波都要拎醫生紙啦"},{"pid":"2906a884fffcf1d04996d49aa791e493ccda6b33","tid":691300,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T15:47:55.000Z","msg":"中出"},{"pid":"87cf428dd249a3046921e1afb2a40d668a0a7ec2","tid":691300,"uid":160555,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T16:31:33.000Z","msg